    "type_D_disj": {
      "name": "Type_D_cores_pairwise_disjoint_pack",
      "proof": [
        "tmult\u22641: each domain point lies in at most one core of the multipad.",
        "\u21d2 C_i \u2229 C_j = \u2205 for i\u2260j.",
        "Packing in D\u2216(U\u222aV) of size n\u22122e: M_pad \u2264 \u230a(n\u22122e)/m_c\u230b (v26/v35)."
      ],
      "statement": "Within a Type D multipad (tmult\u22641), cores are pairwise disjoint. Hence M_pad \u2264 pack_D = \u230a(n\u22122e)/m_c\u230b (after removing U\u222aV). Deployed pack_D = 2.",
      "status": "PROVED"
